
Intelligent E-Commerce Data Analytics Platform
 Overview

This project builds an end-to-end data analytics platform for e-commerce using multiple datasets.
It integrates data processing, visualization, machine learning, and API deployment into a single system.


 Objectives
Data cleaning & preprocessing
Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)
Interactive visualizations
SQL-based analytics
Machine Learning (prediction & classification)
Customer segmentation (RFM)
REST API deployment
 Datasets
E-Commerce Transactions (541K+ rows)
Online Retail Data (541K+ rows)
Customer Shopping Data (99K+ rows)
Product Data (API JSON)
 Tech Stack

Python, SQL, Pandas, NumPy, Scikit-learn, Plotly, Flask, SQLite

